{{羅馬教廷}}

'''宗座宗教協談理事會'''（{{lang-la|Pontificium Consilium pro Dialogo Inter Religiones}}）是[[聖座|聖座]]負責與其他[[宗教|宗教]]交流的機構，現任理事會主席為{{link-en|彌額爾·安傑洛·阿尤索-吉索特|Miguel Ángel Ayuso Guixot}} [[樞機|樞機]] <ref name="Vatican20190525">{{cite press release |title=Rinunce e nomine, 25.05.2019 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2019/05/25/0448/00919.html |publisher=Sala Stampa della Santa Sede |accessdate=2019-08-16 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190816180654/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2019/05/25/0448/00919.html |archivedate=2019-08-16 |language=it |date=2019-05-25 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，現任秘書長為{{link-de|英都尼·賈納卡拉特內·科迪圖瓦庫·坎卡納馬拉格|Indunil Janakaratne Kodithuwakku Kankanamalage}}[[司鐸|司鐸]]<ref>{{cite press release |title=Resignations and Appointments, 03.07.2019 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2019/07/03/190703a.html |publisher=Holy See Press Office |accessdate=2019-08-23 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190823175156/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2019/07/03/190703a.html |archivedate=2019-08-23 |language=en |date=2019-07-03 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==簡介==
理事會建於1964年[[第二次梵蒂岡大公會議|第二次梵蒂岡大公會議]]，這是由於《[[教會對非基督宗教態度宣言|教會對非基督宗教態度宣言]]》以後設立。

==結構==
它包括一個決策機構，諮詢機構和執行機構。

